column1: Definition: Education index is an average of mean years of schooling (of adults) and expected years of schooling (of children), both expressed as an index obtained by scaling with the corresponding maxima.
Source: HDRO calculations based on expected years of schooling and mean years of schooling from UNESCO Institute for Statistics (2020) and other sources. Accessed on 21 July 2020.

column2: Organization for Economic Co-operation and Development
